description: Demolition of the existing one-form entry primary school buildings and erection of a new ten storey building to provide: a replacement two-form entry nursery and primary school at ground and first floor level (for up to 460 children with ancillary community use with opening hours of 07:00 to 21:30 weekdays and 10:00 to 21:00 at weekends); a multi-use games area and playground space at second floor level; 101 residential flats with associated balconies from third to ninth floor level; an open air residential roof garden at tenth floor level; and, ground level landscaping, cycle parking, servicing area/disabled parking and refuse store areas.
